                <note rend="inline" type="source">123 [Stuart, J. Leighton]: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clark</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">at Canton</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-08-02T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 2, 1949—2 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>TelCan 525. Dept this morning released to press statement previously transmitted
                    you re departure Ambassador.<note n="46" xml:id="d971fn46">See telegram telCan
                        No. 513, July 29, <ref target="#pg_807">p. 807</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
